Come on, Harry.

2034
02:28:33,585 --> 02:28:34,586
One minute.

2035
02:28:41,914 --> 02:28:44,289
Thought you were leaving
without saying goodbye, did you?

2036
02:28:48,801 --> 02:28:50,039
This is for you.

2037
02:29:07,252 --> 02:29:08,491
Thanks, Hagrid.

2038
02:29:15,375 --> 02:29:17,144
Go on. On with you. On with you now.

2039
02:29:17,429 --> 02:29:18,234
On with you.

2040
02:29:18,413 --> 02:29:19,663
Oh, listen Harry.

2041
02:29:20,100 --> 02:29:21,982
If that dolt of a cousin of yours,

2042
02:29:22,006 --> 02:29:24,054
Dudley, gives you any grief...

2043
02:29:24,851 --> 02:29:26,195
you could always...

2044
02:29:26,765 --> 02:29:27,699
threaten him...

2045
02:29:27,700 --> 02:29:29,615
