2046
02:29:29,639 --> 02:29:30,699
tail of his.

2047
02:29:30,934 --> 02:29:32,118
But Hagrid,

2048
02:29:32,325 --> 02:29:34,662
we are not allowed to do magic
away from Hogwarts.

2049
02:29:34,996 --> 02:29:36,100
You know that.

